## Contributing

1. Fork the repo and create a feature branch.
2. Keep changes focused — one feature per PR.
3. Run a quick smoke-test before opening a PR:
   ```bash
   pip install -e .
   fm --help
   fm photo_organize /path/to/test/photos
   ```

